ET ACAS API Documentation

Published Date: 5-September-2022 Author: Harpreet Jhita Requirement: API for ACAS Version History: ET ACAS API is added

get.summary: Return a list of CCD case IDs from a provided date

parameters.name: datetime
parameters.description: Format - date time. The date from which the query should return cases which have been modified

get.summary: Return a list of documents on a case
Get a document from CDAM in binary format

parameters.name: documentId
parameters.description: UUID for the document in DM Store

get.summary: Return case data from a list of provided IDs

parameters.name: caseIds
parameters.description: A list of CaseIds to search. Should be comma seperated
